defaultThe Association of Police and Crime Commissioners (APCC) is the national body which supports Police and Crime Commissioners (‘PCCs’) and other local policing bodies.  This document 
defaultco-ordinates 
defaultthe views of PCC
defaults
default in relation to the key areas listed in the terms of reference. The document is arranged in line with those key areas.  
