default5.4
default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultGreater Manchester provides a good example of a PCP making use of its powers of scrutiny through an effective panel comprising 10 local authority leaders. The work of the panel is underpinned by a police and crime steering group which has been able to work jointly with police on achieving consensus where there have previously been diverging views.
