default&#xa0;default10.1
default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultPCCs take transparency very seriously and equate this with empowering communities to hold them to account effectively.  Many have taken steps to improve information about both themselves and the force – for instance, Ian Johnston, PCC in Gwent has launched a PCC App to inform the public about what he is doing, and Sue Mountstevens, PCC in Avon and Somerset, has launched an on-line ‘track my crime’ service for victims.
default&#xa0;
default10.2
default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultPCCs are now publishing their expenses and other related information appropriately.  No national register has been created, in part because of the bureaucracy and complexity involved, but also because most PCCs feel that this is a matter of local accountability. 
default&#xa0;
default10.3
default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
default 
defaultIn addition to equality and diversity within their own offices, PCCs also have a duty to ensure their forces are compliant with their equality duties and that they adhere to the relevant guidance on employment processes and procedures, including recruitment and retention. 
default&#xa0;
default10.4
default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultAll PCCs have now completed their annual registration as Data Controllers, but in any event, the transition provisions in the PRSRA meant PCCs were covered by the former police authority registrations.
default&#xa0;
default10.5
default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultMechanisms to check the accuracy of crime data are in place in all forces, but PCCs are not complacent and know that more can be done.  The current thematic inspection of data integrity by HMIC will be an important step in informing PCCs what more should be done – although several have already put additional steps in place.  For instance, Nick Alston in Essex is setting up an integrity committee, whose terms of reference will include checking force data independently.
